Package au.csiro.pathling.fhir

Class ResourceProviderFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.csiro.pathling.fhir.ResourceProviderFactory
  • @Component
@Profile("server")
public class ResourceProviderFactory
extends Object
    A factory that encapsulates creation of resource specific ResourceProviders. It uses ApplicationContext to create the instances of ResourceProviders so that they are spring beans and as such can be detected by SpringAOP (which is required for the security implementation).
